      </statement>
      <solution>
        <p>We first compute <m>\vec u +\vec v</m>.
          <md>
            <mrow>\vec u+\vec v \amp = \la 1,3\ra + \la 2,1\ra</mrow>
            <mrow>\amp = \la 3,4\ra.</mrow>
          </md>
        </p>

